Defeated for the 12th time in Ligue 1 in 2024/25 on Sunday in Marseille, Le Havre are the fourth team in the 21st century to have at least 12 losses after 16 games in a L1 season after Grenoble in 2009/10, Metz in 2017/18 and Angers in 2022/23.
